Each 1000mg serving delivers 340mg of essential omega-3 fatty acids, 136mg of EPA, 64mg of DHA, along with phospholipids and astaxanthin.,SUPERIOR ABSORPTION FORM: Krill oil's phospholipid form of omega-3s can dissolve in water, allowing it to be better absorbed and more bioavailable compared to fish oils' triglycerides.* Krill oil also avoids the fishy aftertaste and odor associated with fish oils.,SUPPORTS HEALTHY BRAIN, HEART, AND JOINT HEALTH: The omega-3s (DHA and EPA) and astaxanthin found in krill oil have antioxidant properties and help maintain healthy cognitive function, promote cardiovascular health, and support healthy joints and mobility.*,EXTRA PURE, TESTED FOR HEAVY METALS: Our formula is filtered and tested for heavy metals and other contaminants. Every softgel is non-GMO, gluten free, soy free, dairy free, and corn free. There are no artificial ingredients, stearates, or sulfates.,BIOEMBLEM : BioEmblem Krill Oil is sourced from Antarctica and bottled in the USA at an NSF-registered, cGMP-certified facility in California.

name: Life Extension Krill Healthy Joint Formula - Deep Sea Antarctic Krill Oil Supplement with Hyaluronic Acid & Astaxanthin - Joint Comfort, Motion Support & Inflammation Health - Non-GMO - 30 Softgels
feature_bullets: WHAT IS KRILL HEALTHY JOINT FORMULA? - Joint discomfort can stand in the way of even simple everyday tasks. But you don't have to let it slow you down. Life Extension Krill Healthy Joint Formula can help promote your joint comfort and a healthy range of motion by combining the benefits of krill oil, hyaluronic acid and the carotenoid astaxanthin.,PROMOTE JOINT COMFORT AND RANGE OF MOTION - Studies show that the fatty acids found in krill oil are particularly effective for supporting our joint health. Krill Healthy Joint Formula also includes hyaluronic acid to lubricate and cushion against the repeated physical impacts of everyday life and is fortified with astaxanthin for additional support for joint comfort and range of motion.,ONE AND DONE – When it comes to promoting your joint health, we're guessing you don't want to interrupt your routine. Luckily, all it takes is one softgel a day to get all of these joint health-promoting ingredients. And did we mention that they are clinically studied? In one trial, participants began to experience relief from joint discomfort in just 7-14 days, just enough time to schedule your next adventure!,INGREDIENTS MATTER - Sourced using only the finest raw ingredients with the purity and potency your body deserves. This product is certified non-GMO and gluten-free. Manufactured in the USA and a Certificate of Analysis is available for every product we produce.,LIVE YOUR HEALTHIEST LIFE - For over 40 years, we’ve been developing advanced, effective formulas made with the highest standards and based on the latest scientific findings. We believe the answers to a healthier, richer life are within reach and that rigorous scientific research is the path to get us there. Our formulations are created using the exact ingredients and dosages used in the studies that inspired them, ensuring that maximum bioavailability and efficacy are achieved.

name: Simply as-is | 500mg Antarctic Krill Oil | 60 Softgels | Phospholipid Bound Omega-3s EPA & DHA | Naturally High in Powerful Antioxidant Astaxanthin | No Fishy Reflux
feature_bullets: RICH IN OMEGA-3s: Krill oil contains unique phospholipid-bound EPA & DHA, which are beneficial essential fatty acids. Our krill oil has one of the highest levels of phospholipids on the market.,SUPPORTS COGNITIVE, JOINT + HEART HEALTH: Phospholipid-bound DHA and EPA supports maintenance of joint health and cardiovascular health. Krill oil also contains phosphatidyl choline for healthy brain function.,RICH IN ASTAXANTHIN FOR FREE-RADICAL PROTECTION: Contains naturally occurring astaxanthin which is the potent antioxidant that gives krill oil its vibrant red color and helps protect the cells in your body from free radical damage.,BETTER ABSORPTION + NO FISHY REFLUX: Phospholipids increase the bioavailability of omegas, so a smaller quantity of krill oil can deliver high levels of DHA and EPA in your body. The high phospholipid content of our krill oil also helps with better digestion of the oil, preventing those dreaded fishy burps.,SUSTAINABLY SOURCED: Collected from the pristine waters of the Antarctic using responsible practices focused on protecting the krill biomass and Antarctic eco-system.

name: Kori Antarctic Krill Oil Omega-3 1200mg Supplement - Superior Absorption vs Fish Oil/EPA & DHA, Astaxanthin/Supports Heart, Brain, Joint, Eye, & Skin Health / 90 softgels
feature_bullets: THE OCEAN’S SUPERIOR OMEGA: Our sustainably sourced krill oil is a source clinically proven to raise the Omega-3 levels our bodies need and, coupled with other naturally occurring nutrients found in Antarctic krill, it delivers a powerful supplement designed to support heart, brain, joint, eye & skin health.,MOST NATURAL OMEGA-3 FORM: Kori delivers Omega-3s in their most natural phospholipid and triglyceride form, just as you get in a healthy fish diet, for SUPERIOR ABSORPTION vs fish oils and NO FISHY AFTERTASTE. This is because our bodies’ cells already are made of phospholipids so they absorb and digest this form best. Surprisingly, fish oils have triglycerides but lose phospholipids during processing.,NATURALLY MORE NUTRIENTS: Kori is packed full of esential EPA & DHA omega-3 fatty acids and is a natural source of the ESSENTIAL NUTRIENT CHOLINE, found in foods such as eggs and broccoli, for brain and nervous system health. Kori also has the POWERFUL ANTIOXIDANT ASTAXANTHIN.,CERTIFIED SUSTAINABLE: From the #1 global krill oil supplier that is the only global fishery to earn an ‘A’ rating, and for seven years running.,HARNESSING KRILL’S NUTRTION: Krill are at the start of the marine food chain and offer immense nutritional benefits. Advanced harvesting operations help preserve our krill oil quality. Kori is made with non-GMO krill oil & no artificial flavors, colors, or preservatives, unlike many fish oils that require added preservatives or added flavors to hide fishy tastes.

name: ONNIT Antarctic Krill Oil - 1000mg Per Serving - No Fishy Smell or Taste - Packed with Omega-3s, EPA, DHA, Astaxanthin & Phospholipids - Supports Healthy Joints, Brain, Heart, and Blood Pressure

feature_bullets: 3-IN-1 SUPPLEMENT: Just one (1) of our Superba krill liquid oil capsules contains 500 milligrams of EPA & DHA fatty acids as well as phospholipids from sustainably harvested Antarctic krill. Krill oil is a natural source of astaxanthin from algae in their diet, which we’ve boosted the concentrations of in our supplement. Superba Krill Oil is an advanced formulation for superior support.,ONE AND DONE: Our potent formula allows you to simply take one (1) liquid softgel a day with food (or as directed by a qualified healthcare professional). Each bottle of our Krill Oil contains 120 softgels for a four (4) month supply so that you can get the EPA and DHA your body needs.,SAY GOODBYE TO FISHY BURPS: Our easy-to-swallow softgels have no fishy aftertaste and won't cause any fish burps like other lower quality bulk supplements. Our DHA and EPA supplement is non-GMO verified, gluten free, and IKOS 5-star certified. Our omega 3 phospholipid vitamins for adults are the easiest and most convenient one-and-done pure krill oil daily supplements.,MANUFACTURED IN THE USA: Our products are made in cGMP compliant facilities in the United States, using only the best ingredients from domestic & international origins. For us, it's all about quality control - so you can have confidence in your dietary supplements Unlike pure fish oil supplements, our Krill Oil includes Astaxanthin. Plus, our krill oil 500mg softgels are certified sustainable and traceable by the Marine Stewardship Council (MSC).,THE SPORTS RESEARCH DIFFERENCE: Created in 1980, Sports Research is a privately-owned business born from a passion for fitness, wellness, and healing. Our goal is to help people live their best lives through real, research-backed ingredients created for every body — inside and out. We're fully dedicated to sourcing the highest quality products from around the world, backed by third party testing. We all deserve the best in our quest for healthy living. Our mission is to give you just that.

feature_bullets: ANTARCTIC KRILL OIL: Krill is one of the world’s most abundant and sustainable organisms. MegaRed only sources krill from the Antarctic where krill is most abundant.,OMEGA 3 SUPPLEMENT: MegaRed Omega 3 Krill Oil has been shown to significantly increase your omega 3 index in just 30 days. Supportive research has shown that consumption of EPA and DHA omega-3 fatty acids may reduce the risk of coronary heart disease.,HEART HEALTH: MegaRed Omega 3 Krill Oil supplements provide an optimal combination of omega-3 fatty acids and the powerful antioxidant astaxanthin to support heart health in a once daily softgel.,3X MORE PURE: MegaRed with PureTechTM is 3x MORE PURE than regular krill oil. Salts and other impurities are removed to provide the purest krill oil on the market.,NO FISHY AFTERTASTE and EASY ABSORPTION: Krill Oil is carried in a phospholipid form which is better absorbed by the human body and because it's krill oil as opposed to fish oil, MegaRed Krill Oil has no fishy aftertaste or odor.,These statements have not been evaluated by the Food and Drug Administration. This product is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure or prevent any disease.

name: Kori Krill Oil Omega-3 600mg, 180 Softgels | Multi-Benefit Omega-3 Supplement | Superior Omega-3 Absorption vs Fish Oil and No Fishy Burps (Pack of 3)
feature_bullets: THE OCEAN’S SUPERIOR OMEGA: Our sustainably sourced krill oil is a source clinically proven to raise the Omega-3 levels our bodies need and, coupled with other naturally occurring nutrients found in Antarctic krill, it delivers a powerful supplement designed to support heart, brain, joint, eye & skin health.,MOST NATURAL OMEGA-3 FORM: Kori delivers Omega-3s in their most natural phospholipid and triglyceride form, just as you get in a healthy fish diet, for SUPERIOR ABSORPTION vs fish oils and NO FISHY AFTERTASTE. This is because our bodies’ cells already are made of phospholipids so they absorb and digest this form best. Surprisingly, fish oils have triglycerides but lose phospholipids during processing.,NATURALLY MORE NUTRIENTS: Kori is packed full of esential EPA & DHA omega-3 fatty acids and is a natural source of the ESSENTIAL NUTRIENT CHOLINE, found in foods such as eggs and broccoli, for brain and nervous system health. Kori also has the POWERFUL ANTIOXIDANT ASTAXANTHIN.,CERTIFIED SUSTAINABLE: From the #1 global krill oil supplier that is the only global fishery to earn an ‘A’ rating, and for seven years running.,HARNESSING KRILL’S NUTRTION: Krill are at the start of the marine food chain and offer immense nutritional benefits. Advanced harvesting operations help preserve our krill oil quality. Kori is made with non-GMO krill oil & no artificial flavors, colors, or preservatives, unlike many fish oils that require added preservatives or added flavors to hide fishy tastes.
